  "description": "For each floor in LATTICE, list the demotion sources it explicitly permits (demotableBy) and assert canDemote() returns the expected boolean. Negative pairs (random/unrelated sources) MUST return false. This pins the lattice's demotability matrix as the single arbiter — no implicit demotion path may exist outside canDemote().",
